reviews.review_text: Weve ordered from this location many times. Its always been good, quick and employees provide exceptional service. This is one of the best McD locations in the lower mainland in my opinion. And their burgers are huge, look at that Big Mac!

Called in to ask if they had a specific Happy Meal Toy and the person that picked up was extremely courteous and helpful.  I didnt catch his name; however, he went as far as to offer to place the item on hold for me.

For some reason, Richmond locations have better iced coffees than the ones in Vancouver. The workers here actually look like they work hard too, you can really tell by how fast everyone is moving and calling numbers. I frequent mcdonalds in the downtown area and was slightly surprised by this location.

Hi! I just want to take this opportunity and recognize Navneet (team member) from the McDonalds Sweden way branch. She has been kind and excellent with managing the orders. She exactly knows what a customer needs and pack things accordingly. Although I want this review to be anonymous to her but she really deserves this awesome comment!!! From, The extra maple syrup guy!

This location never disappoint me.  Lots of parking spots(may be not belong to the McDonalds but who cares...:-P).  In the restaurant, enough room and not too crowed, or may be I am lucky when I visit every time :-P Waiting time is decent with hot, fresh food.  Never have trouble with the kiosk ordering.  As far as I have no complain.  So I am giving 5 stars. :-)
M c donals is very yes. Amazing customer service would visit again.
Open 24 hours and full menu always available.
Bulking Vegetarian options: Remove the patty, EZ. Food : 5/5 |

Thank goodness for this McDonalds, because the one at ironwood is a joke. Here you actually get youre food on time, correctly made and you speak with the most friendly people. Compared to other locations this one is too notch!

Except 3 or 4 employees were customer service oriented, which I was glad to get. The majority of them at both drive-through windows must be too busy or stressed out for customer service. No greeting, nothing said at all during the whole transaction.

Never in my entire life have I enjoyed a burger quite to this level it tasted almost as though it came right off the grill of your Backyard BBQ I would bring my entire family tree over there rather than sit at home and cook garbage burgers that are bought at the grocery store fresh I must say that in the last couple of years McDonalds has really stepped its game up. I highly recommend this high-end for any kind of business meeting or family get-together there always accommodating even for the less fortunate as you may see theres the occasional sleeping but always friendly homeless person which I think adds to the funk shui of the building.

Havent been to this one before  I was in Richmond shopping and it was convenient  had to park to the side to wait for my order which is fine but  other cars who placed their order after me got theres first  I called the lady who was dropping off the order to the car next to me and I asked her where was my order  and she went got my order and apologized that they didnt see it there ready to go
Best fast food restaurant with the best fries
This a.great place to hangout with friends and family.
good healthy food always

We love this McDonalds! Fast, reliable service. The only time we have something to complain about is when they serve us chicken nuggets that arent piping hot. Everything is usually fresh and delicious. McDonalds is hard to beat when you need something quick and tasty. We especially love the self ordering system. It makes it easier to map out our order instead of embarrassingly fumbling and stuttering at the front desk!

This McDonalds definitely gets a five-star rating.... I go through the drive-thru before sunrise... And the ladies there who serve my coffee through that window always wish me a nice day and even say good morning before they even give me the price total... Even on rainy days when the rain is dripping off the eavesdrop onto their hand they still push out a positive attitude when they dont have to
Customized order made to perfection at late night drive through! Fries freshly fried, cheeseburger still moist w pickles, and McFlurry mixed all the way.
Staff are nice and efficient, team work. At counter,  machine, cell phone orders are all provided. Parking is convenient.

I know McDonalds should be all the same. But this one tasted pretty good. Maybe my wife and I were hungry. But it just tasted fresher. The coffee was less burnt, or not burnt at all. I made a mistake on my mobile order, and they didnt make a big fuss over replacing it.
A reliable and dependable location. 99% of my orders are fast and accurate. And if its not, they make it right. Its a little out of my way but their app makes it so gosh-darned convenient!
Good clean inside staff friendly and knowledgeable. I usally order on the app. Park in one of the designated spots. Check in. Less than 5 its in the sanitized safety n security of my car.

The ice coffee from this McDonalds is always top notch . I get it black, no sugar, no cream. You can taste the freshness. It rivals many independent coffee shops and is way better than the green mermaids. I think this place has such high turnover the coffee never sits around going stale. Best part.. free with a meal!

Their fries are way better than any other McDonalds I have been to. They gave me a lot. They also never messed up on my customized orders and I always get what I ask for. The Chinese Szechuan burger that was here until Canada Day was delicious and it appeared exactly like pictured. Only got issues with the taste of the McDouble.
Great service! Worker named princess was really respectful, and very nice. And food is good too.

They screwed up my order but when I came back for it and ordered for more they ended up not charging me. People make mistakes and it s okay. The staff at this McDonald s own up to their mistakes 10/10 service would come again
Unlike the Vancouver locations there is no added charge for cups or bags.  City of Vancouver should stop helping retailers make more money off consumers. Shameful.

Up all night with close friends, gotta have my Hot Cake fix every now and then.... McGriddles are deadly too.... Weird how such BAD food gives me such satisfaction and help me keep going.... Till the crash of course. Lol
Lovely McDonalds location. Very comfortable interior. Air conditioned well and the staff are polite and lovely. Will visit again next time around the Knight Street area.
Always so friendly, always make my food right and always makes things fresh for my long drive to work at 3am! Such great service! Love coming back here again and again!
Drive through is usually fast and efficient Parking: Unlimited parking spaces Kid-friendliness: No one cares if kids are here
huge place and good service.
Staff are always friendly and helpful, manager is never far to help with any issues. Reliably good food and great service top to bottom
It has a drive thru and service was quick. Food was OK. Parking: Drive thru

I like Mc Donald because of the mobile app so you can pre-order and pick up at store. Even drive through/ in-store pick up or curb side still works. However, here is usually crowded at lunch time. Be prepared for your waiting time.
It was yummy I was hungry and I cam honestly say thank you for bringing back my child hood memories.
Always good and fast service. Small delays on weeekend mornings.
Staff doing there best , and they were great happy folks yesterday going beyond to see their customers happy ,, Thanks for the pleasant experience Becky
Staff was Trans friendly and polite and service was great!!    what more can I say ,oh yeah covid,aware and I appreciate that !!! Thanks Staff  at Richmond McDonalds
Ordered on the app, picked up inside, quick and easy. Despite it being lunch time, the service was quick and accurate
Best Mc Donalds Ive been to. My Mc Chicken was so fresh it was still steaming, the fries were hot and the milkshake machine was working!
Friendly fast service.  Food was fresh and hot. One of the better Mc Donalds.
The very best and fast service for this macdonald. best Coffee ever.
so nice
Their mc flurry candy dispenser thing is broken but instead of saying their icecream machine is broken like every other mcD, they are pouring it by hand. Respect.
Decision food ,fast customer service and great place
This McDonalds is really good. It has auto-mac and is open 24 hours. Moreover is the old style in a big lot.
They dont mess up orders nearly as often as every other fast food place.
We ordered from the app which was very easy and picked it up a couple minutes later.
Never disappointed with curbside pickup. Friendly staff
I was the first #bts meal orderer, but there isnt any phoyocard with the meal, i disappointed
Nice place.
Joyce and Tim were incredibly friendly and helpful during the night shift. Amazing service!
Best McDonald s in all of the lower mainland. Has the best night staff, very friendly. Great place to stop at when working night shift.
Clean and fast service. Can t complain!
Polite with a sense of humor and usually very quick service even on the food!
It s McDonalds.... what can I say, I got what we wanted. The ice cream machine was working which was awesome!
The food here is usually pretty hot and fresh.
One of the rare McDonald s who got my egg McMuffin right Double egg Becuaee no yolk
One of the best locations, but still have terrible coffee
I love McDonalds Vanilla Con. Vege burger ,fries,Orange pekoe tea. Wow service.
Nice place ,very hot food ty
Its Dons. You know what you getting bruh.
Clean restaurant, people working there looks happy,  they were laughing!
Very good location for drive through and meeting friends with cup of coffee
They try their best to provide the best service they could provide. They deserve a raise.
Strange to eat at a table in the Golden Arches post pandemic.All good.Greatcoffee & service.
I was there early in the morning for breakfast: many people inside, but not a lineup. I like that...
good location.. near my work ;p good service... big space for parking
Always busy there at lunch time but the wait time is reasonable
Bridgeport McDonalds is the best. Fast and good.
Fast service, long term staff, one of the best McDonalds.
Fast hot ready to go can I supersize your fries
Friendly service by the team there well done
Good place to get a quick meal. Clean. Good service.
Staffs are very friendly and helpful, I am definitely happy with the visit.
Very quick, effecient and polite staff.
The order was perfect today!
Good & fast service ...the worker are nice friendly and helpful
Ask for extra pancake syrup. Gentleman very nice to accommodate and with a smile too.
Great service. Very Fast. Accurate Orders.
Fast and efficient service. Good dining space.
Good service and food tasted great!
Really great place, went above and beyond despite being busy!
being open 24/7 makes a great place for late night cravings.
Good 24/7 Mcdonalds. Solid place for late night drive through!
Just drive through meal pick up, flawless
We received our order quickly and it was correct
People here are friendly and the service is pretty fast.
Consistency is the key.  They kill it here as always.
Ive always been a McDonalds loyalist. Yes, I love McDs!
Great coffee with excellent food choices and opens early.
Drive through way faster! Employees are very nice
You pretty much know what you are getting when you walk into a McDs.
This is a great McDonalds location and the staff are really friendly
Was Pretty fast for take out in morning.
Relaxing fun atmosphe wonderful place to meet after the gym!
Is good to double check the other before you leave.
Very easy, ample parking, good location.
